{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"科学发簪观","authorCode":"","content":"我知道吧主搞这个软件很辛苦，不应该来吐槽的。但是居然开个程序都问我要管理员权限！不就是发帖吗，有必要申请那么大权限嘛！我有时会在想，这软件除了发帖还偷偷对我电脑干了些什么。软件开发有个叫做最小权限的原则。你拿到了高权限，自己方便了，但会把用户置身于危险境地。你的软件可能本身不会越权做什么事情，但是万一程序被病毒注入了呢？它们借助你获得的权限为非作歹怎么办？所以希望楼主在下一版加以改进。","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2013-04-21 20:04:00","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"百度贴吧","sourceUrl":"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/2282716674","tid":2464},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"管理员权限。。是不是因为程序要写入文件才这么干的、、","floor":2,"pid":4931,"postTime":"2013-04-21 21:20:00","replyCount":2,"signKey":"","source":"百度贴吧","tid":2464,"initComments":{"list":[{"author":"科学发簪观","authorCode":"","content":"我怎么知道是不是啊，这个应用不是吧主开发的么。楼主你还真有心，把.NET代码混淆了。如果是保存数据要写入文件什么的，楼主应该放到AppData文件夹里或者用.NET独立存储的API，而不是安装目录下。如果非要做成绿色软件，是可以放在安装目录，但是这样就不需要安装包让人安装了嘛。<img class=\"tb-smiley\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/jd/j_0050.gif\">","createTime":"2013-04-21 21:40:00","id":1679,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":false,"name":"","code":"","alias":"","description":"","homepageUrl":"/404","group":0,"groupName":"普通用户","isLocked":false,"gender":0,"avatarUrl":"/common/person.jpg","realName":"","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"0001-01-01 00:00:00"}},{"author":"877120274","authorCode":"FD5F2BEFEC","content":"回复 科学发簪观 :插件功能或可解决问题","createTime":"2013-04-22 18:00:00","id":1680,"replyId":null,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"Sunbread","code":"FD5F2BEFEC","alias":"smm","description":"面包君","homepageUrl":"/u/smm","group":1,"groupName":"认证用户","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/user/cfda1a1be4d5.jpg","realName":"孙某某","refBaike":"","isManager":false,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-04-08 05:01:41"}}],"pageInfo":{"total":2,"pageSize":10,"current":1},"total":2,"totalPages":1}},{"author":"